<br>
Andaeryn Windstrider<br>
Druid of the 51st Circle <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uxiggin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Xiggin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(12/29/01 8:30:57 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5119.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: I have Blood Wolf Harness...</span><hr size=1> There are a good number of spoilers out there and it would be wise to go read them.<br>
<br>
Anyway, when Fergul respawns, he will be at the NorthWest corner of the fort. He will immediately start running towards the EW zone. Some people tell you to wait the NorthEast corner to snag him with snare.  I would however recommend to catch him at his respawn point and drag him to the safe point on the platform between the fort and the river.  The safe point assures the lack of roamers.  <br>
<br>
Fergul can be soloed but there is no way you would survive it if you try at the EW zone-in area.  There are simply too many roamers and a simple wolf is enough to make you lose Fergul.<br>
<br>
Xiggix <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.showPrevMessage?topicID=5119.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.showNextMessage?topicID=5119.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5119.topic&index=9><img src=http://www.execpc.com/~msippel/thedruidsgrove/images/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.emailToFriend?topicID=5119.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.threadControl?topicID=5119.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/gfx/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=5119.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=5119.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thedruidsgrovegeneral">General - EQ<option value="thedruidsgrovefrm27">General - DAOC<option value="thedruidsgrovegeneralot">General - OT<option value="thedruidsgrovefrm29">The Druids Circle<option value="thedruidsgrovefrm18">FAQ & Index<option value="thedruidsgrovef